sources: ['US20010006969A1', '2-Allylamino-4-(t-butylcarbamoyl)amino-7-methylthieno[ 3,2-d]pyrimidine hydrochloride', '0736', 'A 4N hydrochloric acid-ethyl acetate solution was added dropwise to a solution of 398 mg (1.3 mmol) of 2-allylamino-4-(t-butylcarbamoyl)amino-7-methylthieno[3,2-d] pyrimidine in ethyl acetate under ice cooling.
